      "comment": "PENNY CALIDO (2) goes very well here starting 18 times for six wins and nine minors. Scored by 4 lengths last time (19.53) in a Grade 5 over 352m at this track. Appeals as a leading chance in this. STAR TURN (8) won by a nose last start when getting around Rockhampton 510m in a dominant 29.59. In form and looks a leading player again. HELLO BILL (1) was below best at his last start when 6th at this track following a win (25.63) there two back. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and a minor placing from 11 starts. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. BLUE BLEND (5) is very honest and looms as a strong winning hope again.",
